column2: an A.M. Eatery////I'm a big coffee drinker and their House Blend is some of the best ever! Another must get are their Molten Chocolate pancakes! Yaaaaas!! Their hash browns are great too
column3: unlike any I've had. The egg white omelet was a bit too greasy in my opinion
column4: but it's rare to find an omelet that isn't.
